Heart Photo Collage Personalized Script Birthday Card

Review Heart Photo Collage Personalized Script Birthday Card – Birthday Cards This item is trending! Heart Photo Collage Personalized Script Birthday Card It’s a great choice Heart Photo Collage Personalized Script Birthday Card See more about itSay Happy Birthday with a love heart photo collage, personalized birthday card. The photo template is set up for you to add your pictures, working in rows from top to bottom. The photo collage holds 29 photos which are displayed in a mix of portrait, landscape and square / instagram formats. The name is lettered in elegant handwritten script and the wording inside is fully editable. You can also edit "Happy Birthday" if you would like the design for a different occasion. A lovely keepsake card which you can frame or put in a memory box to treasure forever. Price:$9.20
